resources.string: Lightweight - Lightweight housework, walking to activities related to everyday life and sitting for several hours. Walks beyond the same activities related to a seduction contract. Up to 3 hours of physical activity per week.
Moderate - Aerobic gymnastics, running, swimming, playing tactics, in addition to activities linked to the lightweight. Up to 12 hours of physical activity per week.
Intense - Moderate intensity cycling, running, skipping rope, playing tennis and beyond activities related to moderate behavior. Over 12 hours of physical activity per week.
